==English==

===Etymology 1===
Old English ''[[goma]]''; confer German ''[[Gaumen]]'', "palate", Old Norse ''[[gomr]]'', "palate".

====Noun====
'''gum''' (''plural:'' '''gums''')
#the [[flesh]] round the [[tooth|teeth]]

